name: Lot of 6
description:

 ~ A  pair of gold-colored earrings that feature an ivory-colored flower on the end with a rhinestone in the middle.

 ~ A  pair of gold-colored earrings that feature rhinestone on the end. 
 ~ A  pair of gold-colored earrings that feature a pink square-shaped stone on the end. 
 ~ A  pair of gold-colored earrings that feature the word love on the end with a rhinestone in the middle of the o.
